    <a href="/admin/notices"  class="fnav-item">📢 공지 <span class="fnav-cnt">47</span></a>
    <a href="/admin/reports"  class="fnav-item">🚨 신고 <span class="fnav-cnt hot">5</span></a>
    <a href="/admin/inquiry"  class="fnav-item">💬 문의 <span class="fnav-cnt warn">8</span></a>
    <a href="/admin/comments" class="fnav-item">💭 댓글 <span class="fnav-cnt">4,102</span></a>
</nav>

<!-- MAIN -->
<div class="page">

    <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
    <div class="ph">
        <div class="ph-left">
            <div class="ph-eyebrow">Control Panel</div>
            <div class="ph-title">관리자 대시보드</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ph-right">
            <div class="ph-date">Today</div>
            <div class="ph-num">06.16</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ALERTS -->
    <div class="alerts">
        <div class="alert al-red">
            🚨 <span>미처리 신고 <strong>5건</strong> — 즉시 검토 필요</span>
            <a href="/admin/reports" class="ab ab-red" style="margin-left:auto;">처리하기 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="alert al-amber">
            ⏳ <span>전문가 승인 대기 <strong>12명</strong> — 검토 후 처리</span>
            <a href="/admin/experts?status=PENDING" class="ab ab-ghost" style="margin-left:auto;color:var(--amber);border-color:#fcd34d;">승인 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="alert al-blue">
            💬 <span>미답변 문의 <strong>8건</strong> — 답변 대기 중</span>
            <a href="/admin/inquiry" class="ab ab-blue" style="margin-left:auto;">답변 →</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- KPI ROW -->
    <div class="kpi-row">
        <div class="kpi kpi-blue">
